<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="enemy-n">enemy <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'enəmi/    美 /'enəmi/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>敌人；仇敌：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>make an enemy of</strong>
与…树敌</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The best way to destroy an enemy is to make him a friend. 
消灭敌人最好的方法是和他成为朋友。</p><footer>——林肯</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>敌兵；敌军：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The enemy was / were forced to escape. 
敌人被迫逃跑。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[正式用语] 大敌；危害物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Ignorance is the enemy of progress. 
无知是进步的大敌。</p></div></div>